{"tid":358093,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人聽過Rurutia嘅歌？","createTime":"2017-08-13T13:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T16:16:16.000Z","uid":40124,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5491f884f863b674ebf5a6b1c887884b7f4deea","tid":358093,"uid":40124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:09:36.000Z","msg":"連登好似未見過人講Rurutia，想睇下有幾多人聽過。<br />\n<br />\nRurutia簡介：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rurutia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FRurutia&d=sV9ypI8ORAQqPoRsufWwoGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c6f0efc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rurutia</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟喺大概十年前左右，無意中喺foxy down咗Rurutia嘅Selenite，一聽之後就一發不可收拾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢嗰種治癒嘅聲線，無論快歌定慢歌都令我放鬆心情，個感覺係其他歌手畀唔到嘅。而且所有歌都係由佢作曲作詞，啲詞好多都寫得好靚，呢個亦都成為我學日文嘅動機。<br />\n<br />\n2010年前佢每年都會出唔少歌，可惜之後因為身體問題愈出愈少，曲風亦有所改變。早兩年轉會，出咗隻single之後，就一直都冇乜消息，之前個page冇咗，新嘅page整咗兩年都未有，facebook冇update過，連間制作公司嘅官網依兩年都係冇update過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近冇嘢做，就打咗封信經FB畀Rurutia，原本以為個page已經冇人打理，點知竟然轉咗已讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/bpxc15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fbpxc15.jpg&h=89a4e031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/QvC5hY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FQvC5hY.jpg&h=3adebcbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分享幾首我覺得好聽嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q7qbe__idtY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq7qbe__idtY&d=sV9ypI8ORAQqPoRsufWwoGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=55725226\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q7qbe__idtY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=excjjs88E10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dexcjjs88E10&d=sV9ypI8ORAQqPoRsufWwoGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=18126b32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=excjjs88E10</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EjVutieC6sM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEjVutieC6sM&d=sV9ypI8ORAQqPoRsufWwoGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=35a1dd23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EjVutieC6sM</a><br />\n<br />\n近幾年我覺得好聽嘅有<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2kJ0LaJ9a2Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2kJ0LaJ9a2Y&d=sV9ypI8ORAQqPoRsufWwoGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b96a1a63\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2kJ0LaJ9a2Y</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s__3_GewdFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds__3_GewdFg&d=sV9ypI8ORAQqPoRsufWwoGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=44172a57\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s__3_GewdFg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9865e46a7b1b3b52487bf202f1fd5133a9e91b","tid":358093,"uid":40124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088f2e7233fb73d70c5dca5bef80fce8c3cc3fca","tid":358093,"uid":6334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"我最鍾意Pluie<br />\n（應該話我淨係聽過Pluie)"},{"pid":"b05d97d7d65a4a838d70d3ebfc3970dfe063b6fd","tid":358093,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鐘意左十幾年<br />\nlost butterfly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /